works.description: One great way which the famous have etched their names in history, and cashed in on their brand values is by associating themselves with luxury brands, and their branded limited edition products. We have recently told you about 2 such custom creations, including Dwayne Wade limited edition Hubot watch, which has Dwayne Wade’s imaging and styling cues incorporated in it, and Nike’s R9 golden boot tribute to Brazilian Footballer Ronaldo. The latest to be joining the bandwagon is the new Chelsea manager Andre Villas Boas,
